text: Tabora is a surname. Notable people with the surname include: *Benigno G. Tabora (1915–2008), Filipino-American veteran of both World War II and the Korean War *Joel Tabora (born 1947), Filipino Jesuit priest and university president *Krizziah Tabora (born 1991), Filipino bowler ==See also== *Tábora (surname)
title: Tabora (surname)
